{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"bbea2f76-ed65-42c8-9575-3e3ca3a12e08","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x switched the default test runner from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP).**\n\nIn 3.x, the SDK defaulted to the VSTest infrastructure, so `vstest.console` could discover tests. Starting in 4.0, MTP is the default — the built test assembly is itself the runner, and the VSTest adapter is no longer included. That's why `vstest.console` finds nothing.\n\n### You have two options:\n\n**Option A** – Re-enable VSTest compatibility by adding `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>`:\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/4.1.0\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n</Project>\n```\n\n**Option B** *(recommended)* – Update your CI to use the new runner directly:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test          # works with MTP out of the box\n# or run the test executable directly:\n./bin/Debug/net8.0/TestProject.exe\n```\n\nOption B is the intended migration path; MTP gives faster startup and built-in parallel/filter support without needing `vstest.console`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"cb375005-f89c-4107-a9fe-17c3618a98b4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, MSTest introduced the \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\" (MTP) as an alternative to VSTest. In MSTest.Sdk 4.0+, the default runner changed from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP).\n\nThis means that by default, MSTest.Sdk 4.x projects no longer generate the VSTest adapter/infrastructure needed for `vstest.console.exe` to discover and run tests. Instead, the test executable itself becomes the test runner.\n\nThe key property is `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` — setting this in the project file re-enables VSTest compatibility if needed.\n\n\nLet me walk through what's happening here.","outputTokens":499,"requestId":"67C4:29F112:1CCB526:206E86C:69FD5481"},"id":"797bb9e2-8e80-44d0-81d4-52c522d9466d","timestamp":"2026-05-08T03:12:13.666Z","parentId":"b26c4e5b-4e7f-4c3b-bcc9-5cbaa508ecb3"}
